A '''holodocumentary''' or '''holo-doc''' was a form of factual (non-fiction) [[Holodrama/Legends|holofilm]]. [[Tri-Nebula Entertainment]] made three holo-docs on the exploits of [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]], one of which was called "[[Eight for Aduba-3: The Saga of the Starhoppers]]."

